Detailed Description

the auto-regressive (AR) computation block

f(t+1) = a(t)f(t) + a(t-1)f(t-1) + ... + a(t-n+1)f(t-n+1) or f(t+1) = a[0]f(t) + a[1]f(t-1) + ... a[n-1]f(t-n+1)
